<hw>Hawe"bake`</hw> <pr>(h⟦add⟧"b⟦amac⟧k`)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<def>Probably, the baked berry of the hawthorn tree, that is, coarse
fare. See 1st <er>Haw</er>, 2.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>
